tal\n|{{Success}}\n|\n|-\n|1959-12-10\n|Jupiter\n|AM-32\n|[[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station|CCAFS]] [[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 6|LC-6]]\n|\n|Missile test\n|Suborbital\n|{{Success}}\n|\n|-\n|1959-12-17\n|Jupiter\n|AM-26\n|[[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station|CCAFS]] [[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 26|LC-26B]]\n|\n|Missile test\n|Suborbital\n|{{Success}}\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n===1960===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0\";\n|-\n! Date/Time<br/>([[UTC]])\n! Rocket\n! [[Serial number|S/N]]\n! Launch Site\n! Payload\n! Function\n! Orbit\n! Outcome\n! Remarks\n|-\n|1960-01-26\n|Jupiter\n|AM-28\n|[[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station|CCAFS]] [[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 26|LC-26B]]\n|\n|Missile test\n|Suborbital\n|{{Success}}\n|\n|-\n|1960-03-23\n|Juno II\n|AM-19C\n|[[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station|CCAFS]] [[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 26|LC-26B]]\n|Explorer\n|Scientific\n|LEO\n|{{Failure}}\n|Third stage failed to ignite\n|-\n|1960-10-20\n|Jupiter\n|CM-217\n|[[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station|CCAFS]] [[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 26|LC-26A]]\n|\n|Missile test\n|Suborbital\n|{{Success}}\n|\n|-\n|1960-11-03\n|Juno II\n|AM-19D\n|[[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station|CCAFS]] [[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 26|LC-26B]]\n|Explorer 8\n|Scientific\n|LEO\n|{{Success}}\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n===1961===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0\";\n|-\n! Date/Time<br/>([[UTC]])\n! Rocket\n! [[Serial number|S/N]]\n! Launch Site\n! Payload\n! Function\n! Orbit\n! Outcome\n! Remarks\n|-\n|1961-02-25\n|Juno II\n|AM-19F\n|[[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station|CCAFS]] [[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 26|LC-26B]]\n|Explorer 10\n|Scientific\n|LEO\n|{{Failure}}\n|Third stage failed to ignite\n|-\n|1961-04-22\n|Jupiter\n|CM-209\n|[[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station|CCAFS]] [[Cape Canaveral Air Force Station Launch Complex 26|LC-26A]]\n|\n|Missile test\n