ole show, and gets even angrier when Ryan secretly invites Jen back for a follow-up show.\n |LineColor       = 87A96B\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|Last Man Standing (season 8)\n |EpisodeNumber   = 165\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 13\n |Title           = Student Doubt\n |DirectedBy      = Leslie Kolins Small\n |WrittenBy       = Pat Bullard\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|5}}\n |ProdCode        = 8ATP12\n |Viewers         = 3.52<ref name=\"8.13\">{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-thursday-cable-originals-network-finals-3-5-2020.html|title=ShowBuzzDaily's Top 150 Thursday Cable Originals & Network Finals: 3.5.2020|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|date=March 6, 2020|work=Showbuzz Daily|accessdate=March 6, 2020}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary    = Mandy enlists help from Vanessa and Jen to coach Kyle on how to study better, knowing Kyle is too proud to admit he's struggling with his college classes. Meanwhile, Chuck and Ed reveal to Mike their superstitious method of deciding what cars to purchase for their restoration business.\n |LineColor       = 87A96B\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|Last Man Standing (season 8)\n |EpisodeNumber   = 166\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 14\n |Title           = This Too Shall Bass\n |DirectedBy      = Andy Cadiff\n |WrittenBy       = Erin Berry\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|12}}\n |ProdCode        = 8ATP14\n |Viewers         = 3.67<ref name=\"8.14\">{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-thursday-cable-originals-network-finals-3-12-2020.html|title=Updated: ShowBuzzDaily's Top 150 Thursday Cable Originals & Network Finals: 3.12.2020|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|date=March 13, 2020|work=Showbuzz Daily|accessdate=March 13, 2020}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary    = With the 25th anniversary of Outdoor Man's \"Big Ass Bass\" festival approaching, Mike tries to convince Bonnie to let Ed stay home instead of going to their planned art festival in Connecticut. Bonnie eventually admits she doesn't 